114
00:04:26,266 --> 00:04:27,476
Jenna Middleton!

115
00:04:27,559 --> 00:04:29,686
Bem-vinda a Degrassi.

116
00:04:31,313 --> 00:04:33,273
Sente-se, Alli.
Certo?

117
