Divirtam-se!

212
00:08:03,150 --> 00:08:05,485
Abra bem a boca,
Clare querida!

213
00:08:11,491 --> 00:08:13,035
(SUSPIRA, PREOCUPADA)

214
00:08:22,461 --> 00:08:23,420
Oi.

215
00:08:23,504 --> 00:08:24,463
