217
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:26,798
(PORTA FECHA)

218
00:08:26,882 --> 00:08:28,926
Tudo bem?

219
00:08:29,009 --> 00:08:30,052
Sim.

220
00:08:30,135 --> 00:08:31,345
Porque eu tenho uma surpresa.

221
00:08:33,972 --> 00:08:36,099
