362
00:14:31,622 --> 00:14:32,581
SKIP:
Claro!

363
00:14:34,249 --> 00:14:35,918
É toda sua,
cara.

364
00:14:36,001 --> 00:14:37,753
Não, Declan, esquece.

365
00:14:37,836 --> 00:14:39,004
Ah, qual é.

366
00:14:39,087 --> 00:14:40,881
